| `gated` | `x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i` | candidate | 门控仍导出到同一静态库和 | 直接兼容 |
| `routed` | `x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i` | candidate | route 只改 support ranking | 直接兼容 |
